          ></iframe>
          <iframe
            class="aspect-[9/16] w-full"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SaPx0Z534HI?si=7fyhTfuIWQy-U4XJ&controls=0&modestbranding=1&rel=0&fs=0&disablekb=1&playsinline=1"
          ></iframe>
          <iframe
            class="aspect-[9/16] w-full"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SaPx0Z534HI?si=7fyhTfuIWQy-U4XJ&controls=0&modestbranding=1&rel=0&fs=0&disablekb=1&playsinline=1"
          ></iframe>
          <iframe
            class="aspect-[9/16] w-full"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SaPx0Z534HI?si=7fyhTfuIWQy-U4XJ&controls=0&modestbranding=1&rel=0&fs=0&disablekb=1&playsinline=1"
          ></iframe>
          <iframe
            class="aspect-[9/16] w-full"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SaPx0Z534HI?si=7fyhTfuIWQy-U4XJ&controls=0&modestbranding=1&rel=0&fs=0&disablekb=1&playsinline=1"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
        <h2
          class="text-[32px] text-white md:text-[42px] font-semibold mb-8 text-center max-w-[800px] mx-auto leading-[40px] mt-[120px]"
        >
          Mira cómo María García consiguió 40 nuevos clientes con nuestro
          sistema:
        </h2>
        <iframe
          class="w-full aspect-video"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SaPx0Z534HI?si=7fyhTfuIWQy-U4XJ&controls=0&modestbranding=1&rel=0&fs=0&disablekb=1&playsinline=1"
          title="Video caso de éxito"
          allow="autoplay; encrypted-media"
        >
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </section>
    <Faqs />
    <img
      class="h-[35px] md:h-[45px] object-contain mx-auto mt-12 mb-8"
      src="/images/cliente-ejemplo.jpg"
      alt="Cliente Ejemplo"
    />
    <p
      class="text-white/80 font-medium text-[16px] md:text-[20px] text-center mb-[80px]"
    >
      © Agencia Ejemplo 2025. Todos los derechos reservados.
    </p>
